prompts.frontCover: Vibrant comic book cover art, dynamic and action-packed scene celebrating a birthday. A woman, styled as a superhero, joyfully soars through a colorful cityscape. She is wearing a sleek, modern superhero suit in shades of deep purple and electric blue. In one hand, she triumphantly holds aloft a magnificent, multi-layered birthday cake with glowing candles. Her other hand is outstretched in a classic superhero flying pose. A man, dressed as her loyal and slightly goofy sidekick in a complementary orange and yellow costume, flies beside her, holding a giant, unwrapped gift box that is bursting with colorful confetti and streamers. They both have exuberant, happy expressions. The background is a stylized city skyline at sunset, with dramatic speed lines and "POW!" and "ZAP!" style sound effect bubbles adding to the action. The entire scene is rendered in a classic comic book style with bold black outlines, halftone dot patterns for shading, and a palette of saturated, primary colors. In the center of the composition, integrated into the artwork, the words "Happy Birthday, Super Lao Lao!" are written in a bold, dynamic, handwritten cursive script with a slight 3D effect. Flat 2D artwork, cinematic lighting, professional illustration.
